# Project Structure

```
magnum-opus/
├── backend/
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── api/                    # FastAPI route handlers
│   │   │   ├── __init__.py         # Router registration (api_router)
│   │   │   ├── smartlead.py        # SmartLead: campaigns, leads, THE webhook handler
│   │   │   ├── crm_sync.py         # CRM sync: GetSales webhooks, contacts, sync triggers
│   │   │   ├── replies.py          # Reply automations: CRUD, approve/send, drafts
│   │   │   ├── contacts.py         # Contact CRUD, activities, status transitions
│   │   │   ├── search.py           # Search pipeline: jobs, queries, results
│   │   │   ├── search_chat.py      # Chat-based search interface (shares /search prefix)
│   │   │   ├── chat_stream.py      # SSE streaming for search chat (shares /search prefix)
│   │   │   ├── operator_tasks.py   # Operator tasks API (3-tab view)
│   │   │   ├── pipeline.py         # Outreach pipeline processing
│   │   │   └── ...                 # Other API modules
│   │   ├── core/
│   │   │   └── config.py           # ALL config lives here. Secrets via .env, NEVER hardcoded.
│   │   ├── models/                 # SQLAlchemy models
│   │   ├── schemas/                # Pydantic schemas
│   │   ├── services/
│   │   │   ├── crm_scheduler.py    # Background loops: polling, webhook setup, reports, recovery
│   │   │   ├── crm_sync_service.py # SmartleadClient + GetSalesClient API wrappers
│   │   │   ├── reply_processor.py  # Reply classification, draft generation, notifications
│   │   │   ├── notification_service.py # Slack + Telegram notification dispatch
│   │   │   ├── smartlead_service.py    # Low-level SmartLead API (rate limiting, retries)
│   │   │   ├── status_machine.py   # Contact status transitions (source of truth)
│   │   │   └── ...
│   │   ├── utils/
│   │   │   └── normalization.py    # Shared: normalize_email, normalize_linkedin_url, etc.
│   │   ├── db/                     # Database engine, session, migrations
│   │   └── main.py                 # FastAPI app, startup/shutdown hooks
│   └── alembic/                    # Database migrations
├── frontend/
│   └── src/
│       ├── api/                    # API client functions (one file per domain)
│       ├── components/             # Reusable React components
│       ├── pages/                  # Page-level components (one per route)
│       ├── lib/                    # Utilities, theme
│       └── App.tsx                 # Route definitions
├── docs/                           # Architecture docs, API docs, data model
├── .cursor/rules/                  # Rules for AI agents (YOU ARE HERE)
└── .env.example                    # Template for environment variables
```

## Key Architectural Decisions

1. **One webhook handler per platform** — SmartLead in smartlead.py, GetSales in crm_sync.py
2. **Centralized webhook registration** — only in crm_scheduler.py
3. **Shared utilities** — normalization in utils/normalization.py, not copy-pasted
4. **Config-driven** — all tunables in config.py, secrets in .env
5. **Status machine** — all status transitions go through status_machine.py

## Deployment

- Server: Hetzner (ssh hetzner)
- Backend: Docker container `leadgen-backend`
- Frontend: Docker container `leadgen-frontend` (nginx serving static dist/)
- DB: Docker container `leadgen-postgres`
- Build frontend: `cd frontend && npm run build`, then `docker cp dist/. leadgen-frontend:/usr/share/nginx/html/`
- Restart backend: `docker restart leadgen-backend`
